| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7729 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5c71a146-3700-50e5-9ff3-7dd7b60edd9f"
